	<SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><FONT size=5>昆山开发区、昆山高新区、花桥经济开发区管委会，各镇人民政府：</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">根据江苏省经信委《关于做好</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年江苏省两化融合管理体系贯标试点推荐工作的通知》（苏经信企信〔</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">〕</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>214</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">号）要求，现在我市开展省两化融合管理体系贯标试点申报工作。具体事项通知如下：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-spacerun: yes"> </SPAN></SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体"><FONT size=5>一、试点企业推荐条件<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、昆山市境内注册的企业，财务状况和运营情况良好。</SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、两化融合工作具备良好基础，成效比较显著，管理规范，对建立两化融合管理体系有需求。</SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、国家级两化融合示范企业、江苏省两化融合示范企业优先申报，两化融合工作成绩突出的江苏省两化融合试点企业也可申报。</SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、具有建立实施管理体系经验的企业，如质量、环境、能源、职业健康安全、信息安全和信息技术服务等，优先申报。</SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 黑体"><FONT size=5>二、申报要求<SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、各申报企业可在中国两化融合服务平台（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><A href="http://www.cspiii.com/"><FONT color=#0000ff>http://www.cspiii.com/</FONT></A></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）下载《工业和信息化融合管理体系要求（国家标准报批稿）》参考学习。并在中国两化融合服务平台（</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>www.cspiii.com/pg</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）江苏省评估分平台实现每年度的自评估。评估结果作为整个贯标过程的重要参考。</SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</SPAN> <SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">申报试点企业应自愿分享试点工作经验和贯标案例。</SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal><FONT size=5><SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</SPAN> <SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">请各申报单位于</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>21</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">日前将申请材料（见附件）纸质版（一式三份）报送市经信委软件与信息化推进科，并将电子文档发送至联系人邮箱。联系人：梁娟，电话：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>57017933</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，邮箱</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>:108437748@qq.com</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，办公地址：祖冲之南路</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>1666</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">号清华科技园科技大厦</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">楼</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US>402</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">室。</SPAN></FONT></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=5></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=5></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''"><FONT size=5>附件：江苏省两化融合管理体系贯标试点企业申请材料</FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=5></FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
